        Harry Potter

        Film series

        Description

        Description

        Harry Potter is a film series based on the eponymous novels by J. K. Rowling. The series is distributed by Warner Bros. and consists of eight fantasy films, beginning with Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone and culminating with Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows Part 2. Wikipedia
        Release date: 20012011
        Box office: Total (8 films); $7.7 billion
        Budget: Total (8 films); $1.2 billion
        Screenplay by: Steve Kloves (14, 68); Michael Goldenberg (5)
